NG0422:255: om dmar lab chung 'khor lo sham bu can //

NG0422:338: sems nyid mi gnang rang byung rig pa nyid //

NG0422:345: mchog gi 'od gsal mtshon pa'i bri thabs ni //

NG0422:350: // tshon ni mthing kha dkar po ser le brgan //

NG0422:352: tshon rnams rjes shing mdzes tshon gtang *//

NG0422:355: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang ngo *//

NG0422:362: phyag g.yas rdo rje g.yon pa me long 'phyar //

NG0422:365: de yi phyi ma'i 'od skor la //

NG0422:367: de yi phyi ma'i 'od skor la //

NG0422:369: de yi phyi yi 'od skor la //

NG0422:372: sku rnams thams cad tshon gang ba //
NG0422:374: sangs rgyas bcu drug ye shes mdangs gsal rtags //
NG0422:375: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis chos nyid stong pa'i rtags //

NG0422:406: phyi nas mchod pa rgyas par bya //
NG0422:407: dpa' bo bcu rnams gyer la gtang *//
NG0422:408: tha ma dpon g.yog gsum pa ni //
NG0422:409: sman gtor lugs bya gsum gsum dgod //
NG0422:410: phyi nang mchod pa rgyas par bya //
NG0422:411: lha mo bcu rnams gyer la gtang *//
NG0422:413: glo ba'i rtsa ni stong la rgyal //

NG0422:477: de nas bde bar gshegs pa thams cad yang dag
NG0422:481: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin no //
NG0422:482: dngos po med pa kun gyi dngos //
NG0422:483: rang byung shar ba kun gyi gzhi //
NG0422:484: rgyu rkyen med pas kun gyi srog / thog mtha' med pas kun gyi skyabs //

NG0422:487: dngos po med pas gsal bar shar //

NG0422:489: rdzas su ma grub ye shes 'od //
NG0422:490: ye shes rtsa lnga rang bzhin dang *//
NG0422:491: spros pa med pas stong pa dang *//
NG0422:493: phyogs ris med pas gdangs la sangs //
NG0422:494: rang bzhin med pas dwangs la stong *//
NG0422:495: byas pa med pas ye shes lam //
NG0422:496: dpa' bo 'bru lnga rang bzhin dang *//
NG0422:497: dngos po med pas shes rab 'char //
NG0422:498: bris pa med pas sna tshogs 'char //
NG0422:499: rang bzhin med pas sna tshogs gsal //
NG0422:500: ye shes yin pas gos pa med //
NG0422:501: lta ba nam mkha' 'dra ste 'gyur ba med //
NG0422:502: sgom pa nyi zla 'dra ste gsal 'grib med //
NG0422:503: spyod pa ser bu 'dra ste ngos gzung med //
NG0422:504: sems nyid bar snang 'dra ste phyogs ris med //
NG0422:505: 'od gsal nyi ma 'dra ste gsal la gdang *//
NG0422:506: rtsa lnga nyi zer 'dra ste 'phel 'grib med //
NG0422:507: 'bru lnga chu gzugs 'dra ste dngos po med //

NG0422:510: dug lnga gsad pa'i thabs chen yang *//
NG0422:511: nam mkha'i mthong nas zhe sdang sbrul nag 'khyug / shes rab ye shes gdangs gsal mda' gzhu dgang *//
NG0422:512: chos kyi dbyings su ye shes mde rtse gtad //

NG0422:515: stong sangs ye shes chen po mda' gzhu'i bdag / skye med dbyings su ye shes mde rtse bstad //
NG0422:516: gnyis med ye shes mda' ni 'gyur med brdeg /
NG0422:517: yid bzhin sgrom bu'i nang na phrag dog spre'u rtse
NG0422:518: // dngos med rang byung chen po'i mda' gzhu dgang *//
NG0422:519: rlung bsgoms nang du hu~m gi mde rtse gtad //
NG0422:520: bde ba ye shes rang byung mda' 'phang ngo *//

NG0422:523: pad+ma dbyings kyi am gi mde rtse gtad //

NG0422:526: spros med ye shes chen po'i mda' gzhu dgang *//
NG0422:527: sra brtan rgya gram lte ba mde rtse gtaud //
NG0422:528: stong pa chen po'i klong du mda' 'phang ngo *//
NG0422:529: chos sku 'gyur med snang ba'i rgyan du shar //
NG0422:530: chos sku ye shes gting gsal 'gyur med cing *//
NG0422:531: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams kyis gtan la 'bebs pa med //

NG0422:533: mkhas pa dge bshes rnams kyis nyams su myong ba med //
NG0422:534: khams gsum sems can rgyud la lhan ne lhag ge gnas //
NG0422:537: dngos po kha dog dbyibs su grub pa med //
NG0422:538: sems nyid 'gyur med ye shes chen po la //
NG0422:539: rtogs shin mthong du kho rang rang las med //
NG0422:540: ye shes rin po che rang 'bar ba las /
NG0422:541: gdams pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o //  // de nas bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NG0422:542: sbyang med rnam par dag pas 'di brjod do //
NG0422:543: dang po phyi bshags rgyas par bya //
NG0422:544: de nas rten gyi dri ma bca' //
NG0422:545: phyi ru man+dal drug byas la //

NG0422:547: gtor ma drug la byin brlabs la //
NG0422:548: ting 'dzin rigs drug lam nas drang *//
NG0422:549: lha mo bcu yis dri ma 'khrud pas dbyung *//
NG0422:551: dkyil 'khor rtsa ru gzhag la khro bo bcu yi bcos pa gtad //
NG0422:552: 'od gsal dkyil 'khor bri la mchod rdzas rgyas par dgram //
NG0422:555: bum pa'i nang du rigs lnga bskyed //
NG0422:556: lha mo bcu rnams gyer la rigs drug lam nas drang *//
NG0422:557: khyod ni zhe sdang las kyi dbang btsan gyis //
NG0422:558: dmyal ba'i nang du ma skyes sam //
NG0422:559: dmyal ba'i nang du skyes srid na //
NG0422:560: ye shes lha mo thugs rje dang *//
NG0422:561: yi dam lha yi byin rlabs kyis //
NG0422:562: tsha grang sdug bsngal bral nas kyang *//
NG0422:563: dmyal ba'i 'jig rten gnas stongs te //
NG0422:564: lha dang slob dpon spyan sngar khug / ser snas yi dwags su skyes srid na //
NG0422:586: ma mo bcu rnams gyer la gshed po dgram //
NG0422:587: dkyil 'khor bcu rnams gyer la sgrib pa bral //
NG0422:588: lha mo bcu rnams gyer la dkyil 'khor gzhug / thub drug tshogs la rdzogs par bya //
NG0422:589: lha dbog sngags dang phyag rgya brtan //
NG0422:590: phyi nang mchod pa rgyas par bya //
NG0422:591: de nas bzlas pa'i dgongs pa ni //
NG0422:592: yi dam thugs kar 'od gsal bsgom //
NG0422:593: 'od 'phros tshe 'das lus la phog / sgrib sbyangs ye shes a ru gyur //
NG0422:594: don ni stong gsal chen por blta //
NG0422:595: brtags pas 'gyur med chos kyi sku //
NG0422:596: de nas spar ba'i dgongs pa ni //
NG0422:597: dag pa sprul sku dam pa yang *//
NG0422:598: snang ba thams cad 'od du lam //
NG0422:599: dngos po thams cad a ru grol //
NG0422:600: a ni ma skyes stong gsal grol //
NG0422:601: mdzad spyod lam du gyer ba yang *//
NG0422:602: chos nyid stong pa'i gzhu brdungs la //
NG0422:603: ye shes gsal ba'i mda' stongs te //
NG0422:604: dbyer med thabs dang shes rab dgang *//
NG0422:605: tshe 'das bag chags tshogs la brdeg / bde ba chen po'i ngang du gsal //

NG0422:607: snang srid stong par phya la la //

NG0422:610: gdangs gsal longs skur spar ba ni //

NG0422:616: chos kyi dbyings su gzhu brdungs pa //

NG0422:618: a dkar ye shes mde rtse blang *//
NG0422:620: stong gsal chen por phya la la //
NG0422:621: ye shes snying po tshad du bskyal //
NG0422:622: snang srid ye shes 'od kyis gang *//
NG0422:624: thams cad bde stong thig ler 'bar //

NG0422:632: nam mkha'i dbyings su a 'od gsal 'phangs la //

NG0422:639: sbyin sreg rgyas par byas la mtshan byang bsreg /

NG0422:718: gdangs gsal ye shes lha mo ni //

NG0422:764: mched pa med par bzhes su gsol //

NG0422:791: dgra bgegs dbang du sdud mdzad pa //

NG0422:814: ye shes khro bo dpa' bo rgyal //

NG0422:841: ye shes khro bo rang byung rgyal //

NG0422:844: gsal ba dril chen rgyal mtshan 'phyar //

NG0422:847: zhe sdang rtsa ba gcod mdzad pa //
NG0422:848: yid bzhin khro chung phyogs bcur 'phro //

NG0422:856: zhe sdang rtsa ba gcod mdzad pa //
NG0422:857: rnam dag khro chung phyogs bcur 'phro //
NG0422:858: dam nyams dgra la ma ra ya //
NG0422:859: ye shes bdud rtsi si li li //
NG0422:860: ye shes khro bo snang ba'i dpal //
NG0422:861: sku la spros med ske tshe gsol //

NG0422:863: sdug bsngal rtsa ba gcod mdzad pa //
NG0422:865: phyogs ris med par rtsa ba gcod mdzad pa //
NG0422:866: snang gsal khro chung phyogs bcur 'phro //
NG0422:867: dam nyams dgra la ma ra ya //
NG0422:868: khyab brdal chen por me re re //

NG0422:872: nyams bskyed byin rlabs bde ba 'di brjod do //

NG0422:878: snod brtag sbyin pa'i thabs chen yang *//
NG0422:880: blo chen yangs la ma sbyin cig / phyogs med 'khyams pa'i skyon du 'gyur //

NG0422:884: ti ri sogs la ma sbyin cig / sgro skur can gyi skyon du 'gyur //
NG0422:886: mgyogs spyod can la ma sbyin cig / khyad du gsad pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NG0422:887: rtog pa can la ma sbyin cig / ngo mi shes pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NG0422:888: rgyud ngan rnams la ma sbyin cig / rang rgyud sreg pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NG0422:889: thos chung rnams la ma sbyin cig / ye 'phangs za ba'i skyon du 'gyur //
NG0422:891: dad can rnams la ma sbyin cig / dge sbyor gcog pa'i skyon du 'gyur //
NG0422:892: btsa' can rnams la ma sbyin cig / chos la rmongs pa'i skyon du 'gyur //

NG0422:894: nyi ma'i snying po sgrib med sems la shar //
NG0422:895: nam mkha'i snying po phyogs med thugs la shar //
NG0422:896: rgya mtsho'i chu gzugs thos med lus la shar //
